A heavy lever protrudes out of the ground. Upon close examination, you can tell that this mechanism activates at least 5 things (possibly doors), with a delayed timer.
There is an inscription on the handle that reads;

Be fleet of foot,
And don't you dawdle, 
If you don't get far,
It's not so awful.

My brothers you'll find,
They form a chain,
Returning you,
to me again.

So pull me now,
And run the gauntlet,
If no success,
The prize you forfeit.
Strange runes and pictographs, likely arcane in nature, have been scorched into the sides of this hide-covered strongbox.
